ir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from an evil day, from an evil night, from an evil moment, from an evil companion, and from an evil neighbor in the final abode.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7554,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/new-muslims-keep-past-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":38185,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: New Muslims keep all previous good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Hakim ibn Hazim reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what do you think of my good deeds which I did in the time of ignorance, such as upholding family ties, freeing my slaves, and giving charity. Will I receive their reward?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/gates-heaven-dhuhur-prayer-sunan\/","url_meta":{"origin":38185,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Gates of Heaven open before Duhur prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Sa'ib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray four cycles after the decline of the sun before noon prayer and he would say, \"Verily, there is a moment in which the gates of 